// Man page for devices
manDevices="DEVICES(1)                       X Shell Manual                       DEVICES(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    devices - used to see what devices are available to use
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>devices</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Display available devices that can be used for operations.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>devices</b>
    List all available devices"